              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">黯火炉心</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/1cfb4a644ede1096bcf61f228e14be0a_7523606418494959393.png",
                "id": "talent59739",
                "key": "天陨预兆",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "天陨预兆"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】战斗开始时，初始附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">火之新生</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/241466b9ccdefb6219ef6bf74cd493e2_9102977647144650649.png",
                "id": "talent56111",
                "key": "火之新生",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火之新生"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>，对所有敌方后台角色造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_912348805805905823.png",
                "id": "talent49465",
                "key": "黯火炉心",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/2cce1877020bad6ed9476a8bb8db436c_2905446877380287259.png",
                "title": "黯火炉心"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着火元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸发</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超载</span>：本伤害+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃烧</span>：本伤害+1，生成回合结束时造成1点火元素伤害的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃烧烈焰</span>]（可用次数1，最多叠加到2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_4550256992080860726.png",
                "id": "talent39790",
                "key": "火元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">穿透伤害</span></strong></p><p>穿透伤害无法受到伤害加成，但是也无法被护盾、伤害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">火之新生</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附属角色被击倒时：</span>移除此效果，使角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">免于被击倒</span>，并治疗该角色到4点生命值。此效果触发后，角色造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>+1。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">免于被击倒</span></strong></p><p>一些效果会使角色在生命值被降为0的时候<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「免于被击倒」</span>，并治疗该角色到一定生命值。<br>此时，角色不被视为<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「击倒」</span>过。（因此，角色所附属的装备和状态不会被弃置，充能也不会被清空。）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_7562207918633844437.png",
